{"tid":385471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"談置業　林奮強指「唔好喺香港住囉」　倡青年到印度、墨西哥、越南發展","createTime":"2017-09-03T08:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T07:00:40.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0db0316e1502936ea2d6fc0de5dcc1d4df6f2e78","tid":385471,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:59:48.000Z","msg":"土地少、上樓難，是香港現今寫照。前行會成員、智庫「香港黃金五十」創辦人林奮強日前出席電視節目時，就被問及年輕人只想有「瓦遮頭」等問題，他強調要支持土地供應。至於實際地方問題，他直言「唔好喺香港住囉，唔好喺香港發展囉」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n林奮強於節目解釋，「我計過，無論你做工做得好，做工做得唔好，基本上都儲唔到首期買樓，如果我哋所有（土地）供應都無增加，呢個唔係應該你諗住長期喺香港、一個好好住嘅地方，（唔係一個）可以養妻活兒嘅地方」。<br />\n<br />\n林奮強又明言「香港絕對，我可以好肯定咁講，唔係一個會令到人開心嘅一個地方」。至於年輕人要發展的地方，他指中國是「世界中少數亮點」的其中一個，印度、墨西哥、越南等地亦有亮點，故「要睇遠啲」。<br />\n<br />\n對於西方國家，林奮強稱西方已非20多年前的人想像般好，尤其「美國夢」是「噩夢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170903/s00001/1504415005675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170903%2Fs00001%2F1504415005675&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9e10cb81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170903%2Fs00001%2F1504415005675&h=cd05c3ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170903/s00001/1504415005675</a>"},{"pid":"b0651ffc30de5b0237827ff61a9294cd92dfda25","tid":385471,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:02:15.000Z","msg":"唔好喺香港住囉"},{"pid":"4b38469c6ff171a66f2794bd95526269da071575","tid":385471,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"亮乜點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662b5c2c8e903782dac755432a0f6b3317c335fd","tid":385471,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:05:12.000Z","msg":"香港淨係比父幹撚同新移民住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dc78d8f8f30189834428ea391a9e7fa1a1fc3e","tid":385471,"uid":45788,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"你班港豬不滿香港樓價高啊？咁搬去其他國家住lor<br />\n<br />\n你班地球人不滿中国人周街大小二便？搬出地球住lor<br />\n<br />\nGoodest logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254d64d278551f02c51bf6c9fbffb8ce645be127","tid":385471,"uid":50674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"每日150個放支那蝗蟲落離<br />\n然後趕香港青年人走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae610f9668224ef4f26ed570f3ae4d1694dd0608","tid":385471,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"冷靜，小心標題誤導！！"},{"pid":"f1a895cdd27b0393a0402c4781fbe1e2c949b6a2","tid":385471,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街有份狂炒樓<br />\n呢個惡劣環境佢有份造成<br />\n根本無資格咁講野"},{"pid":"04b81eb016d32fc52b42056f23436343a96fbfe0","tid":385471,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0a97c44095f4a05472d9f1797a5ac340d7a4801","tid":385471,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:16:33.000Z","msg":"淋糞強"},{"pid":"a1f51d24997eba3622817ae9a9051eb6cda8360a","tid":385471,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"你港共政府搞放逐計劃囉，咁巴閉，整走人都係控制需求嘅措施黎嘅<br />\n<br />\n你估80年後出生嘅真係好想揀係香港出生、享受你D支那人榮耀呀<br />\n<br />\n西方國家大把地方人口老化要新血人，社會又成日覺得思想自由嘅後生整死香港，口講不如行動大家幫下大家啦"},{"pid":"2feaa34af40327a6370264cfb0e0942e095daa09","tid":385471,"uid":73